this_title: 90 Day Fiancé: Before the 90 Days Season 1
trans_title: 到美国结婚去：话说从头 第一季
introduction: Follow couples who have an existing relationship online, but haven't met in person. We'll experience their journey as they travel to the other's foreign country for the first time in an attempt to establish an in-person relationship and start the K-1 visa process.
